steps.html_instructions: Take exit 243 on the left for Mounds Blvd
Keep left at the fork to continue on I-35E S, follow signs for Interstate 35E S

I-35E S turns slightly right and becomes I-35 S
Entering Iowa
Take the I-35 S/I-80 exit toward Kansas City/Council Bluffs/Davenport
Keep right at the fork, follow signs for I-35 S/I-80 W/Kansas City/Council Bluffs and merge onto I-35 S/I-80 W

Keep left at the fork to continue on I-35 S
Entering Missouri
Take exit 8B to merge onto I-29 N toward K C I Airport
Take exit 3B on the left for I-635 S toward Kansas

Take exit 4B to merge onto I-70 W toward Topeka
Partial toll road

Keep left at the fork to continue on I-470 W, follow signs for Interstate 335 S/South Topeka/Wichita
Toll road

Take exit 50 for US-54/US-400 toward Kellogg Ave/Wichita
Toll road

Keep left, follow signs for US-54 W/US-400 W/Wichita and merge onto US-400 W/US-54 W/E Kellogg Ave
Continue to follow US-400 W/US-54 W
Partial toll road

Continue onto US-56 W/1st Ave
Continue to follow US-56 W
Entering Oklahoma
Continue onto OK-3 W/US-412 W/US-56 W/US-64 W

Turn right onto US-412 W/US-56 W/US-64 W/Cimarron Ave (signs for Ciayton N.M W/Dalhart.T X W)
Continue to follow US-412 W/US-56 W
Entering New Mexico

Continue onto NM-21 N/State Rte 199/4th St
Continue to follow NM-21 N/State Rte 199
Turn right to merge onto I-25 S toward Las Vegas
Turn right onto NM-466 N/Old Pecos Trail (signs for Historic US 66)
